                    </div>
                    <span>I do a lot of advanced ActionScripting and development, but I have had a lot of holes missing and things that I did not quite understand. This book fills in the gaps that are left out with other Flash books. This book explains the process and programming in a complete and easy to understand fashion. This books shows and explains the how and the why. <P>This is a great book, even if you are more advanced with ActionScript, you'll find yourself understanding more about it and new ways to develop and program your Flash development projects.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A very useful book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
